The correct answer is-&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;Lax&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;let&amp;#39;s look at the meaning of the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;given word&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;and the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;correct answer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;wary&lt;/span&gt;(adjective): feeling or showing caution about possible dangers or problems.&amp;nbsp;संभावित खतरों या समस्याओं के बारे में सावधानी महसूस करना या दिखाना।
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(48, 51, 54); font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; letter-spacing: 0.2px;&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(48, 51, 54); font-variant-ligatures: no-common-ligatures; letter-spacing: 0.2px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;:&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;I&amp;#39;m a little &lt;strong&gt;wary &lt;/strong&gt;of/about giving people my address when I don&amp;#39;t know them very well.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;​&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;lax&lt;/span&gt;(adjective)&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;without much care, attention, or control. (बहुत अधिक देखभाल, ध्यान या नियंत्रण के बिना।)
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;The subcommittee contends that the authorities were &lt;strong&gt;lax &lt;/strong&gt;in investigating most of the cases.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Hence, the word &lt;strong&gt;L&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ax&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is the most appropriate antonym for &lt;strong&gt;W&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;ary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul style=&quot;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Let&amp;#39;s explore the meaning of other options&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Conservative&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;(adjective): not usually liking or trusting change, especially sudden change. (आमतौर पर बदलाव को पसंद या भरोसा नहीं करना, खासकर अचानक बदलाव।)
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Older people tend to be more &lt;strong&gt;conservative &lt;/strong&gt;and a bit suspicious of anything new.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Canny&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;(adjective): thinking quickly and cleverly, especially in business or financial matters. (जल्दी और चतुराई से सोचना, खासकर व्यापार या वित्तीय मामलों में।)
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;These salesmen are a &lt;strong&gt;canny &lt;/strong&gt;lot.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Alert&lt;/strong&gt;(adjective): quick to see, understand, and act in a particular situation. (किसी विशेष स्थिति में देखने, समझने और कार्य करने के लिए त्वरित।)
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;I&amp;#39;m not feeling very &lt;strong&gt;alert &lt;/strong&gt;today - not enough sleep last night!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The solution is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gather&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The most appropriate synonym for&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Accrue&lt;/strong&gt; is&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;Gather.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;Gather -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(17, 17, 17);  &quot;&gt;Come together.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;For example : &amp;quot;We all gathered for my birthday.&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;option 2&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;is the correct option.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Let&amp;#39;s discuss information about other options:
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Fetter -&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;confine or restrict (someone).

		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;For example : &amp;quot;To prevent a mutiny, the soldiers had no choice other than to fetter their enemies to trees.​​&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Reject -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(17, 17, 17);  &quot;&gt;Dismiss as inadequate, unacceptable, or faulty.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;&quot;&gt;For example :&amp;quot;They got rejected for the job.&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Spank -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(17, 17, 17);  &quot;&gt;Slap with one&amp;#39;s open hand or a flat object, especially on the buttocks as a punishment.&lt;/span&gt;
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;​&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;&quot;&gt;For example : &amp;quot;He was slapped for spilling coffee on the carpet,&amp;quot;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

The &lt;strong&gt;correct answer&lt;/strong&gt; is &lt;strong&gt;Option 2&lt;/strong&gt; i.e.&lt;strong&gt; Share your deepest feelings.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The idiom &amp;quot;Open your heart&amp;quot; means to share your deepest feelings or thoughts with someone else. It suggests a level of trust and intimacy, allowing one to be vulnerable and open.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example: &lt;/strong&gt;After the therapy session, I felt comfortable enough to open my heart to my therapist about my anxieties.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Therefore, the &lt;strong&gt;correct answer&lt;/strong&gt; is- &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Share your deepest feelings.&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 1: Immediately think of something&lt;/strong&gt; - This means to have a thought or idea come into your mind without delay.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 3: Feel relieved because the stress is removed&lt;/strong&gt; - This refers to the feeling of relief or relaxation that comes when a source of stress or anxiety is no longer present.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 4: Could do something very easily&lt;/strong&gt; - This suggests that an action or task can be performed without much effort.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;Combine&amp;#39;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;Putrefy&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; means&lt;strong&gt; to go through decomposition.&lt;/strong&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;The body had &lt;strong&gt;putrefied&lt;/strong&gt; beyond recognition.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;antonyms&lt;/strong&gt; for the word&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;Putrefy&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; are &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;restore, combine, integrate&amp;quot;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Combine&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; means&lt;em&gt; &lt;strong&gt;to come together to form a single unit.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt; The two countries&lt;strong&gt; combined&lt;/strong&gt; against their common enemy.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Therefore we can say that the word&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;Combine&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; is &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;opposite in meaning&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; to the word&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;Putrefy&amp;#39;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Hence &lt;strong&gt;option 3&lt;/strong&gt; is the correct answer.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Scope&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word &amp;#39;Purview&amp;#39; is a noun that means&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;the scope of the influence or concerns of something&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;query&quot; title=&quot;question&quot;&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;query&quot; title=&quot;question&quot;&gt;For example, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;eg deg&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;This &lt;span class=&quot;query&quot; title=&quot;case&quot;&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;query&quot; title=&quot;falls&quot;&gt;falls&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;b db&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;query&quot; title=&quot;outside&quot;&gt;outside&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; the &lt;strong&gt;purview &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;b db&quot;&gt;of&lt;/span&gt; this &lt;span class=&quot;query&quot; title=&quot;particular&quot;&gt;particular&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;query&quot; title=&quot;court&quot;&gt;court&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The marked option &amp;#39;Scope&amp;#39; means&lt;span class=&quot;ILfuVd&quot; lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hgKElc&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;the extent of the area or subject matter that something deals with or to which it is relevant&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;For example, &lt;em&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dictentry&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;dictlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ldoceEntry Entry&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Sense&quot; id=&quot;scope__1&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;GramExa&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;EXAMPLE&quot;&gt;A full discussion of that issue is beyond the &lt;strong&gt;scope &lt;/strong&gt;of this book&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;eg deg&quot;&gt;We can see that&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;eg deg&quot;&gt; &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Scope&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39; can express the meaning of the word &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ILfuVd&quot; lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hgKElc&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Purview&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Hence, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;Option 3&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Durability &lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;the ability to withstand wear, pressure, or damage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Amenities &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;rArr; a desirable or useful feature or facility of a building or place.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stricture &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;eg deg&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;a restriction on a person or activity. It might also refer to a critical remark or instruction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;resplendent&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The most appropriate synonym of the given word &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;luminous&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39; is &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;resplendent&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Luminous&lt;/strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp;that shines in the dark. (अँधेरे में चमकने वाला)
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;a &lt;strong&gt;luminous&lt;/strong&gt; watch...&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Resplendent&lt;/strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp;brightly coloured in an attractive and impressive way. (आकर्षक ढंग से चमकीला; दमकता हुआ, चमचमाता हुआ; देदीप्यमान)
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;My mother looked &lt;strong&gt;resplendent&lt;/strong&gt; in a red silk sari.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;​&lt;u&gt;Correct Answer:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;resplendent.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Let&amp;#39;s look at the meaning of other words:
	&lt;ul&gt;
